parameters.name: IpamResourceDiscoveryId
parameters.description: The ID of the resource discovery instance.

parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description: The maximum number of entries to return on each page. Valid values: 1 to 100. Default value: 10.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description:
The token to retrieve the next page of results.

- Leave this parameter empty for the first query.

- For subsequent queries, set this parameter to the **NextToken** value returned from the previous query.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description:
The ID of the hosted region of the resource discovery instance.

You can call the [DescribeRegions](~~36063~~) operation to get the region ID.

parameters.name: ResourceRegionId
parameters.description: The ID of the region where the resource is located.
